org.osate.aadl2

Interface SystemImplementation

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AObject, Classifier, ComponentClassifier, ComponentImplementation, Element, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, FeatureClassifier, org.eclipse.core.runtime.IAdaptable, NamedElement, Namespace, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, SubcomponentType, System, SystemClassifier, SystemSubcomponentType, Type
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    SystemImplementationImpl

    public interface SystemImplementation
extends ComponentImplementation, SystemClassifier
    A representation of the model object 'System Implementation'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Owned Bus Subcomponent
    • Owned Data Subcomponent
    • Owned Device Subcomponent
    • Owned Memory Subcomponent
    • Owned Process Subcomponent
    • Owned Processor Subcomponent
    • Owned Subprogram Subcomponent
    • Owned Subprogram Group Subcomponent
    • Owned System Subcomponent
    • Owned Virtual Bus Subcomponent
    • Owned Virtual Processor Subcomponent

    See Also:
    Aadl2Package.getSystemImplementation()
